        "ListingOption": {
          "description": "One retained option from a listing `ask` (rank-don't-skip).\n\nA neutral, page-order entry for a parsed listing record \u2014 the shelf the\nranked `answer` was drawn from, kept so a lower-ranked or unrated item (a\npremium/niche option) stays visible rather than deleted. `title` is the\nrecord's heading (or a text lead); `url` its identifying link (absent on a\ntext-led row); `detail` its own text carrying price / rating as extracted.\na2web does NOT reorder these \u2014 any ranking lives only in `answer`.",
          "properties": {
            "detail": {
              "default": "",
              "title": "Detail",
              "type": "string"
